TY  - JOUR
TI  - Estimation of Returns to Scale and the Elasticity of Substitution
AU  - Maddala, G. S.
AU  - Kadane, J. B.
AB  - [This paper concerns itself with the following problem: Suppose the true production function is of the CES type with constant returns to scalle. If we fit an unrestricted Cobb-Douglas production function instead, what is the nature of the bias in the estimate of the returns to scale parameter?]
